cast.original_title: The School for Good and Evil
cast.overview: Best friends Sophie and Agatha navigate an enchanted school for young heroes and villains — and find themselves on opposing sides of the battle between good and evil.

details.biography: Earl Cave (born 2000) is an English actor. He is perhaps best known for his role as Frodo in the TV series 'End of the F*****g World', Dan Kelly in True History of the Kelly Gang and Daniel in Days of the Bagnold Summer. He is the son of musician Nick Cave and designer Susie Cave.
